# 🍽️ Nutrition-Aware Meal Recommendation System

## 🚀 Overview
This project is a machine learning-based meal recommendation system that suggests personalized Indian meals based on user health parameters and nutritional requirements.

The system uses user-specific calorie calculations along with nutritional similarity techniques to recommend balanced and healthy meals.

---

## 🎯 Features
- Personalized calorie calculation using BMR
- Nutrition-aware meal recommendations
- Macro + Micronutrient analysis
- Interactive web application using Streamlit
- Indian food nutrition dataset

---

## 🧠 Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas, NumPy
- Scikit-learn (Cosine Similarity)
- Streamlit

---

## 📊 How It Works
1. User provides health details (age, weight, height, activity level, goal)
2. System calculates daily calorie requirements using BMR
3. Nutritional features (macro + micronutrients) are used to match meals
4. Cosine similarity is applied to recommend the most suitable meals
5. Results are displayed through an interactive dashboard

